## Bootstrap / Freeze Position

The distinction remains:

- shared bootstrap math is reusable
- each candidate has a strategy-specific frozen test object: rules, params,
  thresholds, split boundaries, costs, judgment population, and block policy
- changing those frozen inputs after seeing a result is the overfitting risk

This change addresses that by freezing split boundaries in evidence, pinning
ADX window provenance, and documenting the exact future block policy before any
positive candidate exists.

